/**
 * Configuration Guide:
 * 
 * 1. Initialize EAS in your project:
 *    eas init
 * 
 * 2. Configure for iOS:
 *    - Apple Developer account required
 *    - Create App ID in App Store Connect
 *    - Generate API key for App Store Connect
 *    - eas build --platform ios --auto-submit
 * 
 * 3. Configure for Android:
 *    - Google Play account required
 *    - Download service account key JSON
 *    - Place in project root as service-account.json
 *    - eas build --platform android --auto-submit
 * 
 * 4. Build commands:
 *    eas build --platform android --profile production
 *    eas build --platform ios --profile production
 *    eas submit --platform android
 *    eas submit --platform ios
 * 
 * 5. Status monitoring:
 *    eas build:list
 *    eas build:view <BUILD_ID>
 */
